":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c6669d47fb920278a029afd97b0bdf5c48e528","tid":1751350,"uid":301152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"692cbd9ee7026b3b4b1ea2aef18881daa6724222","tid":1751350,"uid":301152,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4bf301b031c2986da2ec8856df169cbc385c75e4","tid":1751350,"uid":14816,"like":81,"dislike":1,"score":80,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:05:09.000Z","msg":"係咪真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好氹我開心"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:14:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  中醫贏咗<br />\n<br />\n=======<br />\n<br />\n［文字直播]<br />\n［黃埔東 關家倫vs李超宇］<br />\n［票站：葛量洪校友會黃埔學校］<br />\n<br />\n‼️‼️❤️恭喜黃埔街坊成功滅鼠❤️‼️‼️<br />\n<br />\n0059 1號候選人（關家倫）勝出 得票數4,595<br />\n2號候選人(李超宇）得票數3,374 <br />\n係效票少於5票<br />\n<br />\n0048 點完2 號候選人得票數（李超宇）<br />\n2號候選人（李超宇）得票目測3.5箱（3箱滿 1箱未滿）<br />\n<br />\n0029 有投了1 號候選人（關家倫）的票 <br />\n出現於2 號候選人（李超宇）得票堆中<br />\n<br />\n0027 點完1 號候選人得票數（關家倫）<br />\n開始點2 號候選人得票數（李超宇）<br />\n1號號候選人（關家倫）得票目測4.5箱（4箱滿 1箱未滿）<br />\n<br />\n0000 分類完畢 開始計票數<br />\n先點算1號候選人得票數（關家倫）<br />\n<br />\n2348 從懲教送來兩票 與其他選票混合一齊點票<br />\n<br />\n2335 葛量洪票站主任表示有特別（懲教）票箱正在運送途中 暫停點票 待該票箱送到才繼續<br />\n<br />\n［有突發事件再決定開唔開live]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/937160302975020/posts/2825661517458213?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F937160302975020%2Fposts%2F2825661517458213%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=ZQL1o3idxa%2FDGLG1XyUJb1znTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=63aab257\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/937160302975020/posts/2825661517458213?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:20:03.000Z","msg":"以後李超宇唔駛日日十一點幾由北角過嚟黃埔啦。<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><br />\n【即時】(01:07) 在九龍城「黃埔東」選區，1號候選人民主派關家倫以4,595票擊敗2號接替梁美芬的經民聯李超宇。<br />\n<br />\n李超宇得3,374票，無效票為27張，今屆投票人數為7994人，總選民人數為10,345人，投票率為77.2%。<br />\n</span> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/937160302975020/posts/2825809647443400?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F937160302975020%2Fposts%2F2825809647443400%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=ZQL1o3idxa%2FDGLG1XyUJb1znTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=b8c2b542\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/937160302975020/posts/2825809647443400?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"56c812689ae628125cd23445b0434a62824a863d","tid":1751350,"uid":48315,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dacf3ffd167700477783072bb4e371b5a16b1057","tid":1751350,"uid":207077,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:17:50.000Z","msg":"唔好開心得咁早<br />\n以家非建制派攞到既議席<br />\n係上一屆都「並非」由建制派奪取<br />\n姐係只係同上屆一樣咁解"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:20:50.000Z","msg":"好多區都成功搶左個位返黎"},{"pid":"a408072d18fbcf733130ea0666afee7865224c4e","tid":1751350,"uid":48315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb3d909e4a03371c45fd0b482eeffc5c111e7429","tid":1751350,"uid":278765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:17:54.000Z","msg":"關家倫，贏咗李超宇(鼠王條靚)咩？(黄埔東)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:21:02.000Z","msg":"YES"},{"pid":"c94b4a22f0c9c686c0347795f3bc158dc119837c","tid":1751350,"uid":185781,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bf301b031c2986da2ec8856df169cbc385c75e4","tid":1751350,"uid":14816,"like":81,"dislike":1,"score":80,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:05:09.000Z","msg":"係咪真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好氹我開心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:21:10.000Z","msg":"我感動到喊左出黎屌"},{"pid":"b88c30547028cdb7b2d9fff6384d5313dad3a881","tid":1751350,"uid":185781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"434095ee0d51937c3b178d7ce3045da66128dac6","tid":1751350,"uid":27404,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"b54fa0434f7524b6e99968dcf61ae